{"tid":1728464,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"全民抗氧化 抵抗二噁英","createTime":"2019-11-17T01:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T05:00:20.000Z","uid":85822,"like":9,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7f02f104d50f554382a2816c929c7e91e1301e48","tid":1728464,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0AsJpZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0AsJpZC.jpg&h=4f672153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟乃健康撚 有營養＋化學底<br />\n如果用幅射比喻二噁英嘅毒性＋入侵性<br />\n而且係高致癌物<br />\n可以推斷佢係一種強力氧化物 自由基<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人體比自由基氧化嚴重其中一個結果係致癌<br />\n<br />\n因此用<br />\n幅射預防碘-131可以靠食碘片抗131幅射粒子入侵<br />\n二噁英可以靠大家全世界食抗氧化物：<br />\n各大營養產品 入面包含不同種類嘅維他命 薑黃 大蒜素 Q10 均係有效嘅抗氧化物‼️<br />\n<br />\n全民健康撚 一齊食有信譽嘅健康產品<br />\n<br />\n唔明可以問我 教大家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMy TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTreeHoIsGood&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=c1028dbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood</a><br />\n<br />\nMy 健康Channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FtreehoHealthAdvice&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=17b7ffb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice</a><br />\n<br />\nMy 健康討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/THHATalk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTHHATalk&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=003556cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/THHATalk</a>"},{"pid":"e9135498865756579f3c4d163dbba6b347f3cbaf","tid":1728464,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:38:07.000Z","msg":"推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（緊急要人）再唔出嚟幫手下星期黎明行動成效一定會大減<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728462</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7fa4c5389a9da381968a6b81b4c59367fc0a5054","tid":1728464,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:38:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5804891c84474c5be825aa66006a17ac71b90863","tid":1728464,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:38:27.000Z","msg":"全世界推喔"},{"pid":"662ea312a8aace632588219fe75ecaee52ade70d","tid":1728464,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:39:30.000Z","msg":"推喔"},{"pid":"62870fc075db255752c1f434fa0bc63e5837df41","tid":1728464,"uid":125171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:44:23.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n但當大家都大量接觸左二噁英<br />\n再食會有用？"},{"pid":"0ff288576bc9343029079820bb8f70c405af0a6b","tid":1728464,"uid":26971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:46:11.000Z","msg":"具體黎講 姐係食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb03b351b98d9bcaed09ef4de42950aa4a816ed8","tid":1728464,"uid":35649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ff288576bc9343029079820bb8f70c405af0a6b","tid":1728464,"uid":26971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:46:11.000Z","msg":"具體黎講 姐係食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:49:02.000Z","msg":"正常咁食菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f463a9a4f5b3fc71670b27bf2992b6611b55d6","tid":1728464,"uid":85822,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ff288576bc9343029079820bb8f70c405af0a6b","tid":1728464,"uid":26971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:46:11.000Z","msg":"具體黎講 姐係食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:51:31.000Z","msg":"食藍莓 食蘿蔔<br />\n食各大藥房補充<br